caption.body: Freddie Whitman and Michaela Swensen profile San Francisco’s “Godfather of Skating” David G. Miles, Jr. and his Church of 8 Wheels, a place of community and self-expression through roller-skating located in a former Catholic church in the heart of San Francisco.  See "Church of 8 Wheels" by Freddie Whitman and Michaela Swensen, now playing, in the Video Arts Gallery, pre-security, in the International Terminal. http://bit.ly/2iT0paA
